snippet.title: Star Wars-  Jedi Knight  Dark Forces II Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
The Valley of the Jedi:  A Supernova of stars in a fleeting fog, the eradication of an entire star system...remember, It will be your path to the ways of the force.

Lots of mistakes.  Think of this as a first draft
